This document establishes standards for all technical documentation in the project.

## Requirements
All documentation must include:
- 5-digit prefix matching related functionality
- Standard sections (Overview, Requirements, Implementation, Status)
- Version history with timestamps
- Clear ownership and review cycles
- Automated validation checks

## Implementation
1. Create new documents using this template
2. Include all standard sections
3. Maintain consistent formatting
4. Implement automated validation:
   ```bash
   node scripts/documentation-audit/status-checker.js
   ```
5. Review documentation monthly

