**📊 Database Analysis:**
- **Total Tables:** 196+ active tables
- **Schema:** `public` (primary production schema)
- **Owner:** `postgres` (default administrative user)
- **Coverage:** Complete system architecture across all departments
- **Status Management**: Email processing pipeline with visual indicators (received → parsing → AI processing → ready)
- **Modal System**: Integrated modals for email composition, details, AI tools, signatures, and smart replies
- **Authentication**: Supabase authentication integration with fallback mechanisms

**Key Features:**
- **Email Organization**: Tab-based filtering (Inbox: 6 emails, Sent: 1 email, Drafts: 1 email)
- **AI Enhancement**: Background AI processing with real-time progress indicators
- **Search & Filter**: Advanced filtering by status, attachments, content, and sender
- **Bulk Operations**: Multi-select functionality for batch AI processing
- **Email Composition**: Full-featured email composer with signature integration
- **Thread Management**: Conversation grouping and thread analysis
- **Smart Replies**: AI-generated contextual response suggestions

**Database Tables:**
- `esignature_audit`: Tracks cryptographic proof of signatures with columns:
  - `signature_data`: Encrypted signature payload
  - `signature_metadata`: JSON structure with client/user agent details
  - `session_identifier`: Links to authentication logs
  - RLS Policy: Users can only view their own signatures
- `emails`: Main email storage with AI processing columns
- `email_signatures`: User signature management
- `user_management`: User authentication and profile data

**Files Implemented:**
- `client/src/pages/03010-email-management/components/03010-modern-email-management-page.js` - Main email interface
- `client/src/pages/03010-email-management/components/modals/` - Email modals (detail, AI tools, composition, signatures)
- `client/src/pages/03010-email-management/components/status/03010-EmailStatusIndicator.js` - Processing status display
- `client/src/pages/03010-email-management/components/threads/03010-EmailThreadView.js` - Thread management
- `sql/create-email-signatures-table.sql` - Database schema
- `populate-comprehensive-email-test-data.sql` - Test data population

**Status**: Production-ready email management system with comprehensive AI processing capabilities and realistic test data for development and demonstration purposes.

