#### 1350\_ - Vector Search System

- **Vector Search System**: Comprehensive Supabase-based vector search implementation for document similarity search across 100+ disciplines using OpenAI embeddings.
- **Multi-Discipline Support**: Dynamic search criteria management through database configuration, supporting contracts post-award, civil engineering, electrical engineering, mechanical engineering, and extensible to additional disciplines.
- **Integration Components**:
  - Universal search functions for all disciplines
  - Discipline-specific search functions with proper table name mapping
  - JavaScript client libraries for web applications
  - Flowise integration for AI-powered document retrieval
  - Edge Functions for HTTP-based access (alternative approach)
- **Key Features**:
  - Dynamic search criteria stored in database table
  - Automatic function resolution based on table names
  - Support for 1536-dimensional OpenAI embeddings
  - Performance optimization with proper indexing
  - Comprehensive error handling and validation
- **Implementation**: See [1350 Vector Search System](./1350_VECTOR_SEARCH_SYSTEM.md) for system overview, [1351 Vector Search Implementation](./1351_VECTOR_SEARCH_IMPLEMENTATION.md) for setup guide, and [1352 Flowise Vector Search Integration](./1352_FLOWISE_VECTOR_SEARCH.md) for Flowise-specific configuration.

