- **Average Generation Time**: ~3-8 seconds per SOW
- **Success Rate**: >95% (with retry logic)
- **Response Quality**: Professional 5000+ character SOW documents
- **Format Consistency**: 8-9 structured sections always
- **Error Recovery**: Automatic retry with exponential backoff

